&lt;p&gt;BaubleBar is looking for Part-time Technical Designers to support the design team to create technical packs to send to the vendor for samples. Ideal candidates have a strong understanding of jewelry construction, are creative problem solvers, have a strong attention to detail and able to work independently. Candidates should be able to use their background of jewelry and apply that knowledge to the Baublebar brand aesthetic and price points.&lt;/p&gt;
