&lt;li&gt;Provide up to 29 hours per week of Technical Design assistance; will vary based on business need&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Role can be Hybrid with time onsite at our NYC HQ or fully remote (residing anywhere in the United States and authorized to work in the U.S.)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
