&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3-5 years of technical design experience (jewelry/accessory experience required)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s Degree in Jewelry Design, Design, Fine Art, or related degree preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in Illustrator&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work autonomously with strong attention to detail&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong technical drawing abilities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Positive attitude, strong communication skills, and ability to provide/receive constructive feedback&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;All candidates MUST submit a link or attachment including any relevant work and/or a portfolio&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
